{
  "chapter": 27,
  "chapter_summary": "楚留香潜伏在神水宫湖底巨石间，发现有人闯入。三条人影竟是胡铁花、黄鲁直和戴独行，他们为寻楚留香而来。神水宫白衣弟子围攻三人，胡铁花以折铁刀\"八方风雨\"威猛刚烈，戴独行以丐帮打狗棒配合剑法变化，黄鲁直以沉稳剑法应对，三人联手占据上风。胡铁花以言语激怒九妹等年轻弟子，取得心理优势。此时水母阴姬从湖底秘道现身，端坐水柱之上，如白衣观音般法相庄严。宫南燕向水母阴姬禀报三人来历，水母阴姬对戴独行的胆量表示冷笑。楚留香在暗中观察，等待水母阴姬露出破绽的时机。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这地方就是神水宫?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你们既然来了，还会不知道这是什么地方?",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "初次上门的人，自然要先问问是否找对了地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你找对了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "三位是从哪里来的?有何见教?",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_lu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "黄鲁直",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下柳州黄鲁直，这位是丐帮的前辈戴独行戴老爷子，还有一位就是名满天下的胡铁花。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_mei_fu",
      "speaker_name": "白衣美妇",
      "listener": "char_huang_lu_zhi",
      "text": "很好，三位就请抛下兵刃，听候发落吧!",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_mei_fu",
      "text": "抛下兵刃，听候发落?你说的是什么话?我可实在听不懂。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_mei_fu",
      "speaker_name": "白衣美妇",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "蝼蚁尚且偷生，你们何必一心求死?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_lu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "黄鲁直",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_mei_fu",
      "text": "在下等来此无恶意，只不过来找两个朋友。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_mei_fu",
      "speaker_name": "白衣美妇",
      "listener": "char_huang_lu_zhi",
      "text": "朋友?你可知道这里是什么地方?哪里有你们的朋友?",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_lu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "黄鲁直",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_mei_fu",
      "text": "他们自然不是贵宫弟子，只不过是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_mei_fu",
      "speaker_name": "白衣美妇",
      "listener": "char_huang_lu_zhi",
      "text": "这里绝没有外来的人，普天之下，谁也没有你们这么大的胆子，敢趁夜闯入神水宫。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_lu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "黄鲁直",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他们也许并没有来。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_huang_lu_zhi",
      "text": "你以为他们也和你一样都是君子，说的都是老实话?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "九妹",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你们已是将死的人了，我们根本用不着再跟你们说话。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_du_xing",
      "speaker_name": "戴独行",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv_jiu_mei",
      "text": "我老人家也根本懒得跟你们说话，快去叫'水母阴姬'出来吧!",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "九妹",
      "listener": "char_dai_du_xing",
      "text": "好，你们一死，我就带你们去见她老人家。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_mei_fu",
      "speaker_name": "白衣美妇",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "二十年来，从来也没有人敢在此地动武，你们的胆子倒真不小。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_lu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "黄鲁直",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有话好说，何必动手。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv_jiu_mei",
      "text": "若非看你是个女人，这一刀就要你的命了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "九妹",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "刀猛而无劲，气躁而不凝，这样的武功，也敢来卖狂!",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv_jiu_mei",
      "text": "如此说来，你武功必定满不错的了，我倒想瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "九妹",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "正是要你瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv_jiu_mei",
      "text": "招快而无力，气怯而不勇，这样的武功，也敢在我面前卖狂，若非我怜香惜玉，你这只春葱般的小手，早就变成葱花了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_du_xing",
      "speaker_name": "戴独行",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小心些，若非老夫不愿以大压小，你这只春葱般的小手，就要变成葱油饼了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_dai_du_xing",
      "text": "妙极!妙极!刀斩葱花，棍打葱油饼，现在只差黄老爷子的剑挑葱油鸡了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_lu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "黄鲁直",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv_jiu_mei",
      "text": "你们年纪太轻，临敌经验不足，心浮气躁，再打下去，必有伤亡，还是快请你们的宫主出来吧!",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "宫主法身已现，你们还不跪倒参拜?",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "法身?参拜?你难道真以为自己是神仙么?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这狂徒是谁?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "九妹",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "此人自称胡铁花，和他同来的还有'君子剑'黄鲁直、丐帮戴独行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你们三人是否自觉武功不弱，竟敢闯到这里来?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_du_xing",
      "speaker_name": "戴独行",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "在下等功夫虽不惊人，却也还过得去。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水母阴姬",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "此人是谁的门下?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dai_du_xing",
      "speaker_name": "戴独行",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "我老人家出道的时候，她还不知道在哪里呢!你问她，她又怎会知道我老人家的来历?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "此人本是横行两河的独行盗，三十岁后，才改邪归正，投入丐帮，明虽是当时帮主吕南的弟子，其实却是吕南首徒朱明代师传艺，传授武功给他的，是以他入门虽晚，在帮中辈份却很高。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水母阴姬",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "他武功是否已得了朱明真传?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "text": "朱明号称钢拳铁掌，内力之强，掌力之厚，在丐帮中可称空前绝后，他怎么比得上?只不过他本是独行盗出身，是以轻功似乎比朱明还胜一筹，又因他本使的是剑，所以他的棍法中揉合了'七七四十九回风舞柳剑'的变化，在当今丐帮中，可算是第一人了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_mu_yin_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水母阴姬",
      "listener": "char_dai_du_xing",
      "text": "就连朱明，平生也不敢妄入本宫一步，想不到此人的胆子竟比朱明还大。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 331
    }
  ],
